# Introduction of Java

- What is a **statement**?
  A complete command to be executed is a statement. It can include one or more expresssions.

- What is an **expression**?
  An expression is a coding construct, that encapsulates to a single value.

#### Java Code Structure
- Class
  - Basic units of code.
  - Describe data and logic of your program.

- Package
  - Intermidiate logical code aggregation
  - Group of classes

- Module
  - High-level physical code aggregation
  - Group of Packages